{"tid":307701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦喇叭問題","createTime":"2017-07-03T14:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T06:32:08.000Z","uid":49033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26280182bd70757d457ec72843d20eeea6807445","tid":307701,"uid":49033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打<br />\n小弟個電腦喇叭熄左一段時間<br />\n之後開番就勁大聲 加拆聲<br />\n但開耐啲又無事 好正常<br />\n想問點解會咁<br />\n究竟出現咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1350d2ac6ae64a92ecdd263e73e18e7bc69f9ee","tid":307701,"uid":49033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:58:35.000Z","msg":"有無巴打識喇叭既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ec1357fc3aca9f3f1b8cdc691dca19497b256a","tid":307701,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:01:41.000Z","msg":"軟件問題黎 driver問題"},{"pid":"c4a29d1dd40391eded25de9632765ff04fe8a667","tid":307701,"uid":49033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>軟件問題黎 driver問題</blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以詳細小小<br />\n利申：電腦白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510c24c51d0b623dc15b02375bb899567e418c85","tid":307701,"uid":49033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:36:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b79bb3e7f51dcb0aeb8149a0e233aa859e6bb04","tid":307701,"uid":63641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"如果換耳筒，又有無呢個情況先？"},{"pid":"088f7f229cc4d805cddefbfe598998c404cc734c","tid":307701,"uid":49033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果換耳筒，又有無呢個情況先？</blockquote><br />\n無試過<br />\n但我諗應該無<br />\n因為我係一熄電腦<br />\n第二朝一開就會勁大聲加拆聲<br />\n係喇叭較大細聲都無用<br />\n都係勁加聲同拆聲"},{"pid":"992b228127a04848fcd948806d739530374e8a5a","tid":307701,"uid":49033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果換耳筒，又有無呢個情況先？</blockquote><br />\n無試過<br />\n但我諗應該無<br />\n因為我係一熄電腦<br />\n第二朝一開就會勁大聲加拆聲<br />\n係喇叭較大細聲都無用<br />\n都係勁<span style=\"color: red;\">大</span>聲同拆聲</blockquote>"},{"pid":"011a9fc343d52145806594229784270ca1cc6d9b","tid":307701,"uid":63641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果換耳筒，又有無呢個情況先？</blockquote><br />\n無試過<br />\n但我諗應該無<br />\n因為我係一熄電腦<br />\n第二朝一開就會勁大聲加拆聲<br />\n係喇叭較大細聲都無用<br />\n都係勁<span style=\"color: red;\">大</span>聲同拆聲</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n如果換耳筒就無事的話，咁可能係喇叭問題<br />\n試下耳筒，又或者試下個喇叭駁手機又有無問題<br />\n咁起碼知道喇叭問題定電腦問題先丫嘛<br />\n之後先對症下藥"},{"pid":"be4df12a3ea1013f49b1d99a8e0a0ff17142fbf0","tid":307701,"uid":49033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果換耳筒，又有無呢個情況先？</blockquote><br />\n無試過<br />\n但我諗應該無<br />\n因為我係一熄電腦<br />\n第二朝一開就會勁大聲加拆聲<br />\n係喇叭較大細聲都無用<br />\n都係勁<span style=\"color: red;\">大</span>聲同拆聲</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n如果換耳筒就無事的話，咁可能係喇叭問題<br />\n試下耳筒，又或者試下個喇叭駁手機又有無問題<br />\n咁起碼知道喇叭問題定電腦問題先丫嘛<br />\n之後先對症下藥</blockquote><br />\n好 我試一試先<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}